{"tid":1600683,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"馬雲名句摘錄","createTime":"2019-09-28T16:57:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T08:33:25.000Z","uid":222614,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"79824f47ebacf848bfcf5f2d5007d040fae5fafa","tid":1600683,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:57:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uJ5w11Cm3gM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuJ5w11Cm3gM&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8r%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=885f45cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uJ5w11Cm3gM</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n1. AI stands for &quot;Alibaba Intelligence&quot;<br />\n<br />\n2. 99.99% of the predictions that human being had in the history about the future, all wrong.<br />\n<br />\n3. the zero point zero zero percent of the predictions are right by accident<br />\n<br />\n4. people of street smart like us never scared of AI<br />\n<br />\n5. i'm not interested in Mars, i just came back from there<br />\n<br />\n6. if someday there will be an elevator on Himalaya, i will go there to have a look<br />\n<br />\n7. i never worry about things i cannot solve, i let other people solve it. If no body can solve it, just let it be, that's my life<br />\n<br />\n8. Man can never make another man<br />\n<br />\n9. Errors and mistakes are the best assets of human life<br />\n<br />\n10. It is impossible that human can be controlled by machines (Musk: haha)<br />\n<br />\n11. According to science, human cannot create another animal smarter than humans<br />\n<br />\n12. computer may be clever, but human beings are much smarter (Musk: Yet definitely not)<br />\n<br />\n13. We invented computers, i've never seen a computer invented human beings.<br />\n<br />\n14. it's stupid to compete a computer of play Go. Chess is designed for human to human, why a human fights against a computer? So, i never ever played chess or Go with computer<br />\n<br />\n15. in the future, if you want to survive, you have to be LQ, the Q of love<br />\n<br />\n16. it's great to die, yeah you cannot live long (Musk: fight for the light of consciousness)"},{"pid":"b130761adbc8198fbbd1439b3435fdd29d3f7578","tid":1600683,"uid":75432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:59:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">5. i'm not interested in Mars, i just came back from there</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea45921ee012417b70808a69fad22eafbb7edeb","tid":1600683,"uid":308492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:08:35.000Z","msg":"吹水文科佬vs識技術理科佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287105e840084bae8403d7adfe6c794f5912bbc1","tid":1600683,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T23:21:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">想學馬雲咁成功既香港創業家，即刻同我背曬佢</span>"},{"pid":"d5cf732da91fbad9bb53677baa8b3fbc10bb6ce5","tid":1600683,"uid":144001,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:25:44.000Z","msg":"支那人瀨啱袋底就幾百億身家<br />\n早幾年仲笑誠哥 依家誠哥同佢主人隻揪 佢呢？比人充公家產<br />\n仲敢同Elon Musk講未來 屌一個賣雜貨嘅人知閪未來科技咩 誠哥都識去學咩係Ai啦 <br />\n呢條撚屌唔識就學下啦 係到亂up"},{"pid":"4bbe6330e74cb57083a4ff2f55e37ee6c4bdb490","tid":1600683,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T02:18:07.000Z","msg":"死開啦支那人"},{"pid":"618be98f1095336e3eda81ea9b3d5b8ace7ab0fc","tid":1600683,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bbe6330e74cb57083a4ff2f55e37ee6c4bdb490","tid":1600683,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T02:18:07.000Z","msg":"死開啦支那人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T02:21:07.000Z","msg":"邊個踩親你條尾？"},{"pid":"e9d6d65cdd408b9ac08b02cdf5635ce486bf8131","tid":1600683,"uid":193625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T02:25:43.000Z","